import React from 'react'
import "./index.css"
import Card from "./Card"


const App = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Card
                imgsrc="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/03/25/09/30/belgium-4966646_1280.jpg"
                title="A Netflex Origional Series"
                title1="DARK"
            />
            <hr />

            <Card
                imgsrc="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/03/25/09/30/belgium-4966646_1280.jpg"
                title="A Amazon Origional Series"
                title1="White"
            />
            <hr />

            <Card
                imgsrc="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/03/25/09/30/belgium-4966646_1280.jpg"
                title="A MX-player Origional Series"
                title1="Orange"
            />
            <hr />


        </>
    )
}

export default App
